if my fellow employees agree to it.

847
00:58:05,941 --> 00:58:06,775
OFFICE AFFAIR

848
00:58:08,569 --> 00:58:09,862
Just spill already, I'm dying.

849
00:58:09,945 --> 00:58:11,488
Agree! Totally agree!

850
00:58:11,572 --> 00:58:13,240
Who is it? Someone must be sweating.

851
00:58:13,324 --> 00:58:14,909
I've got my popcorn ready. Spill the tea!

852
00:58:14,992 --> 00:58:17,661
Other companies' cheating scandals
are the best. I'm waiting!

853
00:58:17,745 --> 00:58:19,830
Agreed! Vibes on the 8th floor
are weird right now.

854
00:58:19,914 --> 00:58:20,748
Could it be that?

855
00:58:20,831 --> 00:58:21,957
SAEUM's wild, LOL.

856
00:58:22,041 --> 00:58:23,000
An affair?

857
00:58:23,667 --> 00:58:25,711
Someone must be fabricating stories.

858
00:58:25,794 --> 00:58:28,088
But there is no smoke without fire.

859
00:58:28,172 --> 00:58:29,006
I agree too.

860
00:58:29,089 --> 00:58:32,343
I'm dying to know too.
I wish they'd just tell us already.

861
00:58:32,426 --> 00:58:33,969
Since everyone wants it, here it is.

862
00:58:34,553 --> 00:58:35,971
Hey, it's up!

863
00:58:37,556 --> 00:58:38,891
SINCE EVERYONE WANTS IT, HERE IT IS

864
00:58:38,974 --> 00:58:40,851
Here's something no one knew.

865
00:58:40,935 --> 00:58:44,521
SAEUM's male Manager K
and female Manager C from another team

866
00:58:44,605 --> 00:58:45,940
