867
00:58:47,983 --> 00:58:51,237
They divorced, then met again
when Manager C got recruited to SAEUM.

868
00:58:51,320 --> 00:58:53,656
But get this.
Manager C remarried a few months ago,

869
00:58:53,739 --> 00:58:55,574
and things between these two
got sketchy since then.

870
00:58:56,200 --> 00:58:58,535
Manager C joined a project
that Manager K was leading,

871
00:58:58,619 --> 00:59:01,080
they have private meetings,
and even meet up outside of work.

872
00:59:01,163 --> 00:59:02,957
And here's the smoking gun.

873
00:59:03,040 --> 00:59:05,292
When Manager C was in Busan
for a design exhibition,

874
00:59:05,376 --> 00:59:07,586
Manager K actually stayed
at the same hotel!

875
00:59:08,879 --> 00:59:11,674
If you don't believe me,
check if they used to be married first.

876
00:59:11,757 --> 00:59:13,550
RECEIPTS FROM THE SAME HOTEL
ON THE SAME DAY

877
00:59:24,520 --> 00:59:27,815
Manager K is Kang Si-woo,
and Manager C is Choi Soo-jin, right?

878
00:59:27,898 --> 00:59:29,149
They were actually married?

879
00:59:29,233 --> 00:59:32,611
So is Mr. Kang a divorcé
or a homewrecker? Which one is it?

880
00:59:32,695 --> 00:59:33,821
-He's both!
-Holy crap.

881
00:59:33,904 --> 00:59:35,823
I saw the two of them in a car together.

882
00:59:35,906 --> 00:59:37,032
The vibe was weird then too.

883
00:59:37,116 --> 00:59:39,535
It's shocking they were married,
but an affair? It's fake news, right?

884
00:59:39,618 --> 00:59:41,578
They're good at their jobs
and sleeping around too.

885
00:59:41,662 --> 00:59:44,415
Don't tarnish the company's reputation
and just quit together.

886
00:59:50,045 --> 00:59:52,923
[TODAY'S HOT ISSUE] OFFICE AFFAIR

887
00:59:57,261 --> 00:59:58,220
Mr. Kang,

888
00:59:58,804 --> 01:00:00,139
I think you should see this.

889
01:00:07,563 --> 01:00:10,149
SINCE EVERYONE WANTS IT, HERE IT IS!
HERE'S SOMETHING NO ONE KNEW

890
01:00:10,232 --> 01:00:12,609
SAEUM'S MALE MANAGER K
AND FEMALE MANAGER C FROM ANOTHER TEAM

891
01:00:13,235 --> 01:00:14,820
RECEIPTS FROM THE SAME HOTEL
ON THE SAME DAY

892
01:00:27,833 --> 01:00:28,792
Mr. Kang.

893
01:00:35,591 --> 01:00:37,259
You just stay quiet. Don't do anything.

894
01:00:41,889 --> 01:00:43,098
