900
01:00:56,695 --> 01:00:59,281
I'm reporting them for defamation
and distributing falsehoods.

901
01:00:59,865 --> 01:01:00,908
Let's all take a breath.

902
01:01:02,659 --> 01:01:05,954
So is it true that the two of you
were in Busan on the same day?

903
01:01:06,038 --> 01:01:08,499
I was there
on a business trip with my team

904
01:01:08,582 --> 01:01:10,417
for a design exhibition.

905
01:01:10,501 --> 01:01:12,503
Yes, I was the one
who submitted those receipts,

906
01:01:12,586 --> 01:01:14,963
but I never met Mr. Kang
while I was there.

907
01:01:15,047 --> 01:01:18,008
Mr. Kang, I heard
your business trip was to Pohang.

908
01:01:18,092 --> 01:01:20,719
I made an unexpected stop in Busan
because of a buyer's sudden request.

909
01:01:20,803 --> 01:01:22,930
I simply chose
one of our company's partner hotels.

910
01:01:23,806 --> 01:01:26,517
I had no idea where Ms. Choi was staying.

911
01:01:26,600 --> 01:01:29,520
Then is it true
that the two of you used to be married?

912
01:01:29,603 --> 01:01:30,896
-Yes.
-Yes.

913
01:01:34,024 --> 01:01:36,318
To be honest,
it's our policy not to interfere

914
01:01:37,027 --> 01:01:38,821
in such private matters,

915
01:01:39,696 --> 01:01:42,991
so you'll have to personally file
for a police investigation or lawsuit.

916
01:01:43,617 --> 01:01:46,995
So you're telling us to suffer through
everyone gossiping about us?

917
01:01:47,079 --> 01:01:48,956
It'll die down in no time.

918
01:01:49,039 --> 01:01:51,875
What if someone
spread this rumor with ill intent?

919
01:01:53,961 --> 01:01:54,962
Who would do that?

920
01:01:55,045 --> 01:01:57,005
That's for the company to find out.

921
01:01:57,089 --> 01:01:59,800
Internal corporate receipts were leaked.

922
01:01:59,883 --> 01:02:01,844
Shouldn't the Audit Team investigate that?

923
01:02:03,011 --> 01:02:05,055
Right. I'll look into that.

924
01:02:13,105 --> 01:02:14,231
Where are you?

925
01:02:21,113 --> 01:02:23,615
Totally groundless! What a load of crap.

926
01:02:23,699 --> 01:02:26,034
Anyone who's seen Manager K would know

927
01:02:26,118 --> 01:02:28,704
he's just a workaholic who is cold as ice.

928
01:02:31,582 --> 01:02:34,001
You knew the two of them
used to be married?

929
01:02:35,169 --> 01:02:36,044
Yeah.

930
01:02:37,588 --> 01:02:39,089
You really have nerves of steel.

931
01:02:39,673 --> 01:02:41,008
Me? Not at all.

932
01:02:41,800 --> 01:02:43,469
I'm completely dazed right now.

933
01:02:44,261 --> 01:02:45,637
You're K, right? Hahaha.

934
01:02:45,721 --> 01:02:48,682
I'm not. And just believe it
when I say it's not true, man.

935
01:02:50,267 --> 01:02:52,186
I don't think this will blow over easily.

936
01:02:52,728 --> 01:02:54,938
I heard from a friend on the HR team

937
01:02:55,022 --> 01:02:57,107
that it's not easy
to remove posts from Blah Blah.

938
01:02:59,902 --> 01:03:00,861
Actually…

939
01:03:01,987 --> 01:03:04,698
I was with Mr. Kang that day.

940
01:03:04,781 --> 01:03:06,241
The day they were supposedly at the hotel?

941
01:03:06,575 --> 01:03:07,409
Yeah.

942
01:03:08,952 --> 01:03:11,538
A burglar broke into my place,
so Mr. Kang came back to Seoul.

943
01:03:12,915 --> 01:03:14,583
If I reveal this,

944
01:03:15,834 --> 01:03:17,127
it'll clear up the affair rumor, no?

945
01:03:17,211 --> 01:03:18,337
Are you insane?

946
01:03:19,922 --> 01:03:21,507
Why would you get involved?

947
01:03:22,466 --> 01:03:24,927
The second you get involved,
you'll be the target.

948
01:03:25,636 --> 01:03:28,931
You shouldn't even cough too loudly
when a promotion's on the line.

949
01:03:29,014 --> 01:03:30,933
Just close your eyes, cover your ears,

950
01:03:31,016 --> 01:03:32,851
and wait for this storm to pass. Okay?

951
01:03:34,686 --> 01:03:36,730
MR. KANG, I THINK YOU SHOULD SEE THIS
WHERE ARE YOU?

952
01:03:40,150 --> 01:03:41,068
What's the story?

953
01:03:41,944 --> 01:03:44,196
-About what?
-Mr. Kang and Ms. Choi.

954
01:03:44,279 --> 01:03:46,573
You guys on the task force
must know something.

955
01:03:46,657 --> 01:03:47,616
Yeah, we know.

956
01:03:47,699 --> 01:03:50,452
We know Mr. Kang is so busy
he doesn't have time for an affair.

957
01:03:50,536 --> 01:03:51,995
Come on, that's a different matter.

958
01:03:52,704 --> 01:03:55,499
No matter how busy you are,
you can still sleep together.

959
01:03:55,582 --> 01:03:56,416
Exactly.

960
01:03:56,500 --> 01:03:59,127
You can stay at the same hotel
with a work trip as an excuse.

961
01:04:00,546 --> 01:04:02,089
You two do that, then.

962
01:04:02,172 --> 01:04:04,424
But please stop running your mouths.

963
01:04:06,802 --> 01:04:09,137
All right, let's just go order.

964
01:04:09,888 --> 01:04:12,099
You can only sit once you've ordered.

965
01:04:15,102 --> 01:04:16,895
Please, hold back.

966
01:04:20,691 --> 01:04:22,901
I came out for some fresh air.
I'm on my way back.

967
01:04:39,668 --> 01:04:41,962
Did you go to her hotel room,

968
01:04:42,045 --> 01:04:43,839
or did Ms. Choi come to yours?

969
01:04:44,840 --> 01:04:47,259
Why did you split up
if you were going to get involved again?

970
01:04:50,345 --> 01:04:53,640
What, do you get off
on a forbidden relationship?

971
01:04:54,391 --> 01:04:56,018
Is this pathetic little card

972
01:04:56,101 --> 01:04:57,603
