973
01:04:58,520 --> 01:05:00,856
I have no idea what you're talking about.

974
01:05:02,691 --> 01:05:03,650
What? Huh?

975
01:05:03,734 --> 01:05:05,611
Are you going to hit me? Hit me, then!

976
01:05:05,694 --> 01:05:08,196
We have a crowd already.
Hit me! Come on!

977
01:05:08,280 --> 01:05:09,156
Huh?

978
01:05:09,865 --> 01:05:11,575
Ms. Choi and Mr. Kang

979
01:05:11,658 --> 01:05:13,118
were not together that day.

980
01:05:14,786 --> 01:05:16,705
How could you possibly know that?

981
01:05:17,414 --> 01:05:19,499
Because I was the one
who was with Mr. Kang.

982
01:05:21,918 --> 01:05:22,878
What?

983
01:05:42,272 --> 01:05:43,357
Mr. Kang and I

984
01:05:44,483 --> 01:05:45,442
are dating.

985
01:05:57,788 --> 01:05:58,997
Is this your answer

986
01:05:59,831 --> 01:06:00,832
to my marriage proposal?

987
01:06:10,842 --> 01:06:11,677
Yes.

988
01:06:58,974 --> 01:07:01,393
SPECIAL THANKS TO BAE YU-RAM

989
01:07:29,504 --> 01:07:31,339
I thought the lies would disappear

990
01:07:31,423 --> 01:07:33,175
once I told the truth.

991
01:07:33,258 --> 01:07:34,176
You should brace yourself.

992
01:07:35,051 --> 01:07:37,596
Is there a chance
Cha Ji-yoon seduced him on purpose?

993
01:07:37,679 --> 01:07:39,973
People are more cruel than you'd think.

994
01:07:40,056 --> 01:07:41,099
But don't let them break you.

995
01:07:41,183 --> 01:07:42,851
I'm still the same.

996
01:07:42,934 --> 01:07:44,144
Can you say with certainty

997
01:07:44,227 --> 01:07:47,981
that no personal feelings
affected your judgment?

998
01:07:48,440 --> 01:07:51,067
How would you feel
if I got sent to an overseas office?

999
01:07:52,027 --> 01:07:53,987
Someone filed a complaint
against Mr. Kang.

1000
01:07:54,070 --> 01:07:55,363
Have you lost your flipping mind?

1001
01:07:55,447 --> 01:07:57,073
Why is there so much noise these days?

1002
01:07:57,157 --> 01:07:59,659
Let's get rid of Ms. Cha.

1003
01:08:05,916 --> 01:08:07,918
Subtitle: Yenny Kang
